summary: Abhinay Cherupally is a passionate data scientist and blogger with a strong background in artificial intelligence and machine learning. He is the founder of Techabhee.com and has been creating SEO-friendly content since 2020. Abhinay has collaborated with Intel and holds certifications in Machine Learning, SEO, and Data Science Foundations. He is dedicated to tech education and growth, and has demonstrated his ability to create engaging, SEO-optimized blog content that effectively boosts website traffic. Abhinay is also skilled in using various programming languages such as Java, Python, and Linux, and has experience with tools like AWS, Streamlit, and Flask.

Jaswanth Reddy Vulchi is a highly skilled Computer Science Master's graduate with a strong focus on software development and DevOps. He has demonstrated expertise in various programming languages such as Core Java, Python, Swift UI, React, and Swift. His experience includes working as a Site Reliability Engineer, where he implemented CI/CD pipelines, improved system reliability, and enhanced security. He also has a strong background in machine learning, having applied algorithms like Random Forest, KNN, and K-Means Clustering to VANETs for predictive analytics. Additionally, he has published a Docker course on Udemy and has a strong research background, as evidenced by his high ResearchGate statistics.
